                    (drafting notes)&lt;/title&gt; &lt;/heading&gt; &lt;seclaw:bodytext&gt;
                    &lt;seclaw:level leveltype="section"&gt; &lt;seclaw:bodytext&gt;
                    &lt;h&gt;Parties&lt;/h&gt; &lt;h&gt; &lt;emph typestyle="it"&gt;Read more about
